      • AngleComparing

        public static boolean AngleComparing(double DirectionA,
                                     double DirectionB)
        this method is to compare the two directions the key is to get in which way an object turn from A direction to B direction is faster
        参数:
        DirectionA - DirectionA
        DirectionB - DirectionB
        返回:
        return true if clockWise, false if counterClockWise

      • Guiding

        public static int Guiding(Object A,
                          Object B)
        Guide method is important for missle guide and AI aiming its an application of getRelativeAngle
        参数:
        A - Object needs guide
        B - Target
        返回:
        return 1 if need turn clockWise, -1 if need turn counterClockWise
